SQL_STMT_U.val: select IMQD_IMQH_ADMNO, IMQD_IMQH_CLNTNO, IMQD_IMQH_TYPE, IMQD_LINENO, B.IMQI_INVO_NO from :5/imqd a INNER JOIN :5/IMQI b ON b.IMQI_IMQH_ADMNO=a.IMQD_IMQH_ADMNO AND b.IMQI_IMQH_CLNTNO=a.IMQD_IMQH_CLNTNO AND b.IMQI_IMQH_TYPE=a.IMQD_IMQH_TYPE AND b.IMQI_LINENO=a.IMQD_LINENO INNER JOIN :5/INVO c ON c.INVO_NO=b.IMQI_INVO_NO where a.IMQD_IMQH_ADMNO=:1 AND a.IMQD_IMQH_CLNTNO=:2 AND IMQD_IMQH_TYPE=:3 AND IMQD_LINENO=:4 order by c.INVO_DUEDATE, c.INVO_INVOICENO
